Version:        %_version
Release:        0
Summary:        Wayland Compositor Infrastructure
License:        MIT
Group:          Development/Libraries/C and C++
Url:            http://wayland.freedesktop.org/

#Git-Clone:	git://anongit.freedesktop.org/wayland/wayland
